result.name: goodwin-sands-marine-conservation-zone-mcz-survey-infauna-data-2014
result.notes:
**CEND0114**

Counts and presence/absence of species of macrofauna identified from 15 grab 
samples collected at Goodwin Sands Marine Conservation Zone between the 25 and 
18th January 2014

**CEND0614**

Counts and presence/absence of species of macrofauna identified from 46 grab 
samples collected at Goodwin Sands Marine Conservation Zone between the 11th 
April and 8th May 2014

**2GDK71014**

Counts and presence/absence of species of macrofauna identified from 30 grab 
samples collected at Goodwin Sands Marine Conservation Zone between the 22nd 
September and 2nd October 2014
